&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Risk UX team helps users understand, manage, and improve their risk standing on Stripe. We craft exceptional product experiences to help users navigate all of Stripe’s risk journeys (i.e. information collection to meet partner/regulatory commitments). These risk experiences are some of Stripe’s most critical user journeys – allowing us to seamlessly onboard users to the global financial ecosystem and apply targeted actions to stop fraud. The Risk UX team delivers these journeys at scale (i.e. millions of users) and partners with teams across Stripe to ensure we deliver consistently excellent user experiences via flexible UX partners, primitives, and APIs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
